white: Having a harem in your basement.
Killing your crush and his whole family.
Ranting to your child about how you can't wait for both of you to die.
Believing that Calne Ca deserves love.
Setting your father's house on fire and holding him at gunpoint.
Cutting off people's arms and planting them in a garden.
Abandoning your child in a house in the woods.
Dying in place of your sister.
Killing everyone with green hair because your crush doesn't like you back.
Sending an entire village to sleep.
Crying every time "The Last Revolver" plays.
Thinking that a doll is your step-daughter.
Killing your sister with a pair of scissors.
